# ar_session_error_code_data_provider_failed_to_run

**Enumeration Case**

The error code for when a data provider fails to run.

## Declaration

```swift
ar_session_error_code_data_provider_failed_to_run
```

## Determining the cause of session errors

- **ar_session_error_code_data_provider_not_authorized**: The error code for when a data provider is missing at least one authorization it needs to run.
